headline: Keysight Introduces Scale-Up Validation Solutions for AI Data Centers
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., February 18, 2026--New validation solutions enable data center operators to overcome bandwidth, latency, and interoperability challenges as AI infrastructure scales.

headline: Unlocking Q1 Potential of Keysight (KEYS): Exploring Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics

headline: Camtek (CAMT) Misses Q4 Earnings Estimates
summary: Camtek (CAMT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -2.02% and +0.72%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
